    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The colorful world of <strong>Cosminomy</strong> offers simple yet engaging <strong>turn-based strategy</strong> mechanics. Succeed as a space colonist by building sufficient structures on <strong>gridless planetary</strong> surfaces. Manage your <strong>resources</strong> wisely and expand your colony to new worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a spacelord by developing superior tactics, or simply enjoy the <strong>relaxing gameplay</strong> and <strong>cozy aesthetics</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113400/extras/94773ed5db2ab0eac5882ab0a89040fb.poster.avif?t=1766005343\" width=622 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113400/extras/94773ed5db2ab0eac5882ab0a89040fb.webm?t=1766005343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113400/extras/94773ed5db2ab0eac5882ab0a89040fb.mp4?t=1766005343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT GAMEPLAY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No grids or tiles, only free building.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Populate little planets with various facilities. Utilize their unique mechanics by selecting optimal locations for them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form efficient relations between neighbouring buildings to turn local valuables into great profits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No time pressure. Advance step by step.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each building placement represents a new turn, when all your incomes are calculated. Invest wisely in the next facility to steadily grow your infrastructure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No deck mechanics, you decide what to build next.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113400/extras/ddcdfdd9809e65539af53be871bbb3da.poster.avif?t=1766005343\" width=622 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113400/extras/ddcdfdd9809e65539af53be871bbb3da.webm?t=1766005343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113400/extras/ddcdfdd9809e65539af53be871bbb3da.mp4?t=1766005343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather scientific data from colonized planets and spend it on new discoveries.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No unit management and battles, but you can pop clouds with the cursor.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Advance from planet to planet, estabilishing a multigalactic economy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each biome has different challenges and valuables for your colony. Cosminomy is more about adaptation than terraforming.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you respect the natives or sacrifice their homes for the greater profit?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosminomy Early Access is expected to <strong>launch in 2026</strong>. Add to wishlist and stay tuned for updates!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113400/extras/183c6b746b100c1d744d413bf86dd27a.poster.avif?t=1766005343\" width=622 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113400/extras/183c6b746b100c1d744d413bf86dd27a.webm?t=1766005343\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113400/extras/183c6b746b100c1d744d413bf86dd27a.mp4?t=1766005343\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
